on right click:
    if player's tool is potion:
        cancel event

        set {_item} to player's tool

        set {_effects::*} to potion effects of {_item}

        loop {_effects::*}:
            apply loop-value to player

        remove 1 of {_item} from player's inventory

        send "&a포션 효과가 즉시 발동되었습니다!" to player
